  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2781020/extras/c36bacaba4f3564241a562e000145020.poster.avif?t=1723036737\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2781020/extras/c36bacaba4f3564241a562e000145020.webm?t=1723036737\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2781020/extras/c36bacaba4f3564241a562e000145020.mp4?t=1723036737\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Small Living World </strong>is a complete <u>ecosystem simulator</u>. It simulates everything from the <u>full-water cycle</u>, through <u>plant growth</u>, to the <u>animal reproduction</u>.<br>Every pixel is simulated, everything counts. Watch it evolves by itself, or manipulate the system.<br>At the beginning, you have access to a limited number of plants and animals. Populate your world to unlock more advance life forms. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2781020/extras/d06259c3022e64eec0484fa7bd3d4297.poster.avif?t=1723036737\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2781020/extras/d06259c3022e64eec0484fa7bd3d4297.webm?t=1723036737\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2781020/extras/d06259c3022e64eec0484fa7bd3d4297.mp4?t=1723036737\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2781020/extras/6941318b30957bb4f9ca7af4b3c9b91f.webp?t=1723036737\" width=264 height=48 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2781020/extras/be639b9dc5a30899daf56c69dea353cd.avif?t=1723036737\" width=600 height=108 /></span><br>Create different <strong>biomes</strong> with selected <u>plants</u> and <u>animals</u>. Add <u>decorative objects</u> to complete your vision. But be careful, not all combination will succeed. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2781020/extras/3db4df1a194994f4ae8d07cf45f3e001.webp?t=1723036737\" width=364 height=50 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2781020/extras/ca38dd7ad3011946cc3e4db28916a18f.poster.avif?t=1723036737\" width=424 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2781020/extras/ca38dd7ad3011946cc3e4db28916a18f.webm?t=1723036737\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2781020/extras/ca38dd7ad3011946cc3e4db28916a18f.mp4?t=1723036737\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>In Small Living World, <u>everything</u> can be <strong>transformed</strong>. From the ground level, up to the mountains, down to the sea, you have the control over everything. And you know, with great power comes great responsibility.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2781020/extras/f6773516d4c4af335d82bd9bbae6d724.webp?t=1723036737\" width=253 height=52 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2781020/extras/9cb9ddc8633e749715523973ef021fdf.webp?t=1723036737\" width=600 height=48 /></span><br>Figure out the best environment to make them thrive. Elements like sun light, water, ground and surrounding area affect the growth. Visual icons will help identify their requirements.<br>Once seeded, they will propagate through your world. Be careful where you add them.<br>Generated pixel per pixel, each plant is unique.  <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2781020/extras/e938fa17f348e46a3abed7fd3b05ca9c.webp?t=1723036737\" width=274 height=50 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2781020/extras/964e677ec9023ae967c469ebef290c0f.webp?t=1723036737\" width=600 height=48 /></span><br>22 living animals available to populate your world. Each has their own <strong>behavior</strong> and <strong>needs</strong>. As living entities, they <u>require food</u> and <u>water</u>. Some will feed on vegetables, some others are less friendly.<br>Be sure they have plenty of food before introducing them to your world. It is not easy to maintain the preys / predators balance. <br>If you are more adventurous, you can even unlock<strong> fantasy creatures</strong>.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2781020/extras/8261fd7d98f7f00790e5a28599913c6d.webp?t=1723036737\" width=333 height=50 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2781020/extras/55728d7df9febcf0c707d93cb0aa52cf.webp?t=1723036737\" width=600 height=48 /></span><br>22 objects available to decorate your world. Objects aren't only decorative, some of them possess <strong>hidden features</strong>. Try and see if you can guess what they do.<br>Structures <u>age overtime</u>. Their appearance slightly changes as the decades past. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2781020/extras/ee1fb0be1c27e1982912babc34b0b484.webp?t=1723036737\" width=222 height=44 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2781020/extras/a6e07d580d06c239f563d56748ec18df.avif?t=1723036737\" width=600 height=64 /></span><br>For your convenience, the game also includes a <strong>Sandbox Mode</strong> <u>without any limitation</u>.<br>It first needs to be <u>unlocked</u> from the standard game to prove your competencies.",
