ounding area affect the growth. Visual icons will help identify their requirements.<br>Once seeded, they will propagate through your world. Be careful where you add them.<br>Generated pixel per pixel, each plant is unique.  <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2781020/extras/e938fa17f348e46a3abed7fd3b05ca9c.webp?t=1723036737\" width=274 height=50 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2781020/extras/964e677ec9023ae967c469ebef290c0f.webp?t=1723036737\" width=600 height=48 /></span><br>22 living animals available to populate your world. Each has their own <strong>behavior</strong> and <strong>needs</strong>. As living entities, they <u>require food</u> and <u>water</u>. Some will feed on vegetables, some others are less friendly.<br>Be sure they have plenty of food before introducing them to your world. It is not easy to maintain the preys / predators balance. <br>If you are more adventurous, you can even unlock<strong> fantasy creatures</strong>.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2781020/extras/8261fd7d98f7f00790e5a28599913c6d.webp?t=1723036737\" width=333 height=50 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2781020/extras/55728d7df9febcf0c707d93cb0aa52cf.webp?t=1723036737\" width=600 height=48 /></span><br>22 objects available to decorate your world. Objects aren't only decorative, some of them possess <strong>hidden features</strong>. Try and see if you can guess what they do.<br>Structures <u>age overtime</u>. Their appearance slightly changes as the decades past. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2781020/extras/ee1fb0be1c27e1982912babc34b0b484.webp?t=1723036737\" width=222 height=44 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2781020/extras/a6e07d580d06c239f563d56748ec18df.avif?t=1723036737\" width=600 height=64 /></span><br>For your convenience, the game also includes a <strong>Sandbox Mode</strong> <u>without any limitation</u>.<br>It first needs to be <u>unlocked</u> from the standard game to prove your competencies.",
